---
import thumbnailImage from '../../public/SLS-assets/video-thumbnail.png';
---

<section class="py-20 bg-white" id="priming">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-12">EcoDenser Priming Tutorial</h2>
    
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="aspect-video rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
          <video
            controls
            class="w-full h-full"
            poster={thumbnailImage.src}
          >
            <source src="/sls-website/SLS-assets/ecodenser.mp4" type="video/mp4">
            Your browser does not support the video tag.
          </video>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            The video represents an initial priming of the EcoDenser. Every time an experiment is changed out, 
            crimp the water lines to avoid draining the unit. This should allow for expedited priming.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>